name: Boeing 747-400LCF Dreamlifter Landing and Taxi at Paine Field ᴴᴰ
description:
Two Paine Field videos in one day! :D
Here's one of Boeing's 747-400LCFs or "Dreamlifters" landing at Paine Field in Everett, WA. It was always a pleasure to see these birds when I was there. They may not have the lines of a regular 747 but they're still awesome to look at (mainly because you're wondering how the heck does this thing fly, lol). Hope you enjoy!

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
